  "detailed_description": "<span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><img class=\"bb_img\" src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/1837220/extras/850c9a84fb9990debc93fd29bdb01623.avif?t=1765931167\" width=640 height=82 /></span><br>In the game \"<strong>Psalm 5:9-13</strong>\" you have to plunge into a terrifying place, at first glance it is quite normal, but the further you go, the more it reveals its essence. This horror game is a first-person walking simulator with a VHS effect and a tense atmosphere, explore the location, find anomalies, and move on. Frightening things will await you along the way, are you ready to face THIS?<br><br>The average time to complete the game is 30 minutes<br><br><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><video class=\"bb_img\" autoplay muted loop playsinline poster=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/1837220/extras/b723c61f6a565ac7adaa1dbba2304808.poster.avif?t=1765931167\" width=668 height=316 ><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/1837220/extras/b723c61f6a565ac7adaa1dbba2304808.webm?t=1765931167\" type=\"video/webm; codecs=vp9\"><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/1837220/extras/b723c61f6a565ac7adaa1dbba2304808.mp4?t=1765931167\" type=\"video/mp4\"></video></span><h2 class=\"bb_tag\" >Game Features:</h2>-Walking simulator<br>-VHS filter<br>-High quality sounds<br>-Realistic graphics",
  "about_the_game": "<span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><img class=\"bb_img\" src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/1837220/extras/850c9a84fb9990debc93fd29bdb01623.avif?t=1765931167\" width=640 height=82 /></span><br>In the game \"<strong>Psalm 5:9-13</strong>\" you have to plunge into a terrifying place, at first glance it is quite normal, but the further you go, the more it reveals its essence. This horror game is a first-person walking simulator with a VHS effect and a tense atmosphere, explore the location, find anomalies, and move on. Frightening things will await you along the way, are you ready to face THIS?<br><br>The average time to complete the game is 30 minutes<br><br><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><video class=\"bb_img\" autoplay muted loop playsinline poster=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/1837220/extras/b723c61f6a565ac7adaa1dbba2304808.poster.avif?t=1765931167\" width=668 height=316 ><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/1837220/extras/b723c61f6a565ac7adaa1dbba2304808.webm?t=1765931167\" type=\"video/webm; codecs=vp9\"><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/1837220/extras/b723c61f6a565ac7adaa1dbba2304808.mp4?t=1765931167\" type=\"video/mp4\"></video></span><h2 class=\"bb_tag\" >Game Features:</h2>-Walking simulator<br>-VHS filter<br>-High quality sounds<br>-Realistic graphics",
